001package com.commercetools.graphql.api.client;
002
003import com.netflix.graphql.dgs.client.codegen.BaseSubProjectionNode;
004import java.lang.String;
005import java.util.ArrayList;
006import java.util.List;
007
008public class LocalizedEnumValueProjection<PARENT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>, ROOT extends BaseSubProjectionNode<?, ?>> extends BaseSubProjectionNode<PARENT, ROOT> {
009  public LocalizedEnumValueProjection(PARENT parent, ROOT root) {
010    super(parent, root, java.util.Optional.of("LocalizedEnumValue"));
011  }
012
013  public LocalizedStringProjection<LocalizedEnumValueProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> labelAllLocales(
014      ) {
015     LocalizedStringProjection<LocalizedEnumValueProjection<PARENT, ROOT>, ROOT> projection = new LocalizedStringProjection<>(this, getRoot());
016     getFields().put("labelAllLocales", projection);
017     return projection;
018  }
019
020  public LocalizedEnumValueProjection<PARENT, ROOT> key() {
021    getFields().put("key", null);
022    return this;
023  }
024
025  public LocalizedEnumValueProjection<PARENT, ROOT> label() {
026    getFields().put("label", null);
027    return this;
028  }
029
030  public LocalizedEnumValueProjection label(String locale, List<String> acceptLanguage) {
031    getFields().put("label", null);
032    getInputArguments().computeIfAbsent("label", k -> new ArrayList<>());
033    InputArgument localeArg = new InputArgument("locale", locale);
034    getInputArguments().get("label").add(localeArg);
035    InputArgument acceptLanguageArg = new InputArgument("acceptLanguage", acceptLanguage);
036    getInputArguments().get("label").add(acceptLanguageArg);
037    return this;
038  }
039}
